Titolo: The Legend of Heroes: Trails to Azure

Anno: 2011

Descrizione: The Legend of Heroes: Trails to Azure, known as Ao no Kiseki in Japan, is a 2011 role-playing video game developed by Nihon Falcom. The game is a part of the Trails series, itself a part of the larger The Legend of Heroes series. Trails to Azure continues the story of The Legend of Heroes: Trails from Zero (2010), completing the "Crossbell arc", named after the location in which they take place.
Trails to Azure first released in Japan for the PlayStation Portable in 2011, with no release outside of Asia until an English release was announced a decade later. Based on a fan translation, it is scheduled to be released for Microsoft Windows, PlayStation 4, and Nintendo Switch in 2023.